data.text:
LIMITED EDITION BONE COLOURED VINYL

Release Date: 18th September 2020

A collection of B-Sides and alternate versions of fan favourites pulled from the band’s personal archives. These recordings encapsulate the raw and energetic vibrancy of this brilliant band who cross-over emo, pop-punk and indie-rock effortlessly.

FFO: Jeff Rosenstock, Into It. Over It., Modern Baseball, PUP
